<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Payment Failed</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #E9F1FF;
      background-color: #0A1A2F;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #0A1A2F;
      padding: 40px 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #132742;
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid #1E3555;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #0F2540;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #1E3555;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #1E90FF;
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    h1 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #FFFFFF;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .subtitle {
      text-align: center;
      color: #A8B5C8;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .action-button {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #EF4444;
      color: #FFFFFF;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 16px 0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
    }
    .error-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #EF4444;
      color: white;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #1E3555;
      color: #64748B;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">Voyo</div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <div style="text-align: center;">
          <span class="error-badge">Action Required</span>
        </div>
        <h1>Payment Failed</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">We couldn't process your payment for order {{orderId}}.</p>
        
        <p style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px; color: #E9F1FF;">
          This can happen for a number of reasons, such as an expired card or insufficient funds. Don't worry, you haven't been charged.
        </p>

        <p style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px; color: #A8B5C8;">
           Please check your payment details and try again to activate your plan.
        </p>

        <a href="{{appUrl}}/checkout/retry/{{orderId}}" class="action-button">Try Payment Again</a>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p style="margin: 0 0 10px;">This is an automated notification from Voyo.</p>
        <p style="margin: 0;">&copy; 2024 Voyo. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
